{"tid":1557762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連登有幾多位巴絲已經畀狗拉咗？","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T12:21:39.000Z","uid":2429,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd05affaed3083e24e47049612e520321f33634","tid":1557762,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"幾日前入完臭格 有小小建議想比各位手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556875\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啱啱又見到位巴打畀狗拉咗，好奇想知連登到底有幾多位手足已經中咗招。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就中咗暴動同襲擊他人導致身體傷害。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1193066464114790/posts/2396204647134293/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1193066464114790%2Fposts%2F2396204647134293%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=58c7d16e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1193066464114790/posts/2396204647134293/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果有手足唔想出名但有問題都可以搵我幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n@ymkdcoffice"},{"pid":"dbf3c31265c32aaf1332dae1be7fc1d5f842e586","tid":1557762,"uid":60299,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6283db0eb06d5c2b10e16f5b21d798947bdd9717","tid":1557762,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd05affaed3083e24e47049612e520321f33634","tid":1557762,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"幾日前入完臭格 有小小建議想比各位手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556875\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556875</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啱啱又見到位巴打畀狗拉咗，好奇想知連登到底有幾多位手足已經中咗招。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就中咗暴動同襲擊他人導致身體傷害。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fa